26
00:02:03,110 --> 00:02:08,580
The Health Insurance Portability and
Accountability Act, or HIPAA Privacy Rule,

27
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:13,380
protects PHI held or
transmitted by a covered entity.

28
00:02:13,380 --> 00:02:14,770
And the Department of Health and

29
