35
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:49,940
The expert must also
document the methods and

36
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:52,180
results that lead to this determination.

37
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:59,060
The Safe Harbor Method stipulates
