47
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:44,150
The most straight forward method

48
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:48,420
is completely removing
the problematic variables.

49
00:03:49,970 --> 00:03:54,490
However, this could negatively affect
the usability of the data set for

50
00:03:54,490 --> 00:03:55,840
secondary analysis.

51
00:03:57,070 --> 00:04:02,750
