66
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:08,620
done using a pre-planned
anonymization scheme.

67
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:12,520
An anonymization scheme
describes modifications

68
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:16,940
to the qualitative dataset to
protect respondent confidentiality.

69
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:22,960
For example, a proper name should be
replaced with more generalized text

70
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:26,290
