of the individual or

71
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:28,260
the person's relationship
with the respondent.

72
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:32,430
Specific dates, especially birth dates or

73
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:36,730
important events, will also need to
be replaced with general markers.

74
00:05:37,740 --> 00:05:42,720
Other types of information that
would uniquely identify a respondent

75
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:46,190
may have to be redacted or
removed completely.

76
00:05:47,210 --> 00:05:48,150
In this case,

77
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:52,350
a marker should indicate that an item
was removed from the data set.

78
